OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy start with
OL,6,Fthe odd light shower around. Then all
OL,7,Fareas will gradually brighten up
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon with some sunny
OL,9,Fspells developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight. Some prolonged
OL,13,Fspells of evening sunshine leading to
OL,14,Fsome clear spells overnight meaning it
OL,15,Fmight feel chilly in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
