OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry with lengthy bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells and feeling slightly
OL,7,Fwarmer. Sunshine turning hazy later as
OL,8,Fhigh cloud spreads southeast. Cloudier
OL,9,Fwith the odd spot of rain in the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fstart Monday with patchy rain, then
OL,14,Fdrier, brighter later. Similar for
OL,15,FTuesday and Wednesday with cloudy
OL,16,Fstarts and patchy light rain, before
OL,17,Fwarm sunny intervals develop through
OL,18,Fthe afternoons.
